{"word":"G338 - ἀναίτιος - anaítios - an-ah'-ee-tee-os - Blameless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναίτιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anaítios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ah'-ee-tee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Blameless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குற்றமில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"guiltless, innocent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G159 - αἴτιος - aítios - ah'-ee-tee-os/159\">G159</a> (in the sense of <a href=\"#/G156 - αἰτία - aitía - ahee-tee'-a/156\">G156</a>); <i>innocent:</i> - blameless, guiltless.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}